reviewText: This product arrived late, and none of the movies work on any of our game systems or DVD Players.  The video loads with an error message:  WRONG REGION.  I don't know if I'll get my money back or not, as I threw all three DVDs away since they were garbage from the start.  Awful seller, awful product.
Doesn't work at all! Very disappointed.
Will not play on our DVD player.... My daughter was heartbroken
It's awful!  Was not compatible with any of the DVD devices we had.  Refund please!!!
Terrible, it is not compatible in the US, want my money back.
